{"tid":554541,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇火木八？好似好多人食","createTime":"2018-02-08T15:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T06:28:37.000Z","uid":73094,"like":11,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"106a2f3b921c3ef7403d6eb5c1aeced246146756","tid":554541,"uid":73094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"真心唔明點解咁撚多人食依間垃圾<br />\nD 野又唔係抵食 又少野食 服務態度差到極點<br />\n<br />\n話說頭先我個fd諗住去cwb 食依間垃圾<br />\n點知一出lift 比個新移民呀嬋waitress 嚇窒左<br />\n佢勁大聲鬧個女仔客 係咁大鬧死八婆x n 咁多次<br />\n仲話人地冇錢食唔好黎 仲要惡形惡相<br />\n心諗 大仲以為去左茶記<br />\n<br />\n真係第一次見咁既服務態度 <br />\n人地睇完唔岩食 咪走囉<br />\n唔通仲要比錢食受氣 仲要養埋你條廢柴咩 都憨鳩<br />\n<br />\n利申：平時都唔點食泡菜野 食日本野多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9733d06ecb16ce10d2fedb1ee03049bb31d6fa49","tid":554541,"uid":142771,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次兩個人食左九百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe57afbe862901f193be87c7b91d5b6de7936266","tid":554541,"uid":90663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"去過第間木八食 服務都真係好差 個個閪口閪面 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6be3e9192d5a2220f9e087b6bd43949aa3564f","tid":554541,"uid":76808,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:24:14.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70d67cbcf6e9884eb201fd01acdebccf64d5a21","tid":554541,"uid":73094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe57afbe862901f193be87c7b91d5b6de7936266","tid":554541,"uid":90663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"去過第間木八食 服務都真係好差 個個閪口閪面 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:24:53.000Z","msg":"未食過 見到d 臭閪都唔想幫襯<img src=\"/